hopobject.body: How many days will it take for the cheque to clear? west pharmacy hours roanoke va Hunt is played by Australian heart-throb Chris Hemsworth, but it is the German actor Daniel Brühl in the role of Lauda who really shines, uncannily mimicking the Austrian’s accent and mannerisms. “I was very impressed,” Lauda says of Brühl’s performance. “I couldn’t believe how well he [impersonated me]. He was even worse than I was. '---- you!’ '---- this!’ He did a very good job.
